General.Name: Godsinlosen Nordic AB
General.Description: Godsinlösen Nordic AB (publ) provides various solutions for handling returns and complaints to e-retailers, producers, and distributors in Sweden, rest of European Union, and internationally. It also offers complete circular claims settlement process to the insurance industry. In addition, the company is involved in the collaboration with insurance, logistics, and e-commerce companies that provides logistics, inventory, and damage verification solutions to consumers. Its services include GIAB Circular Platform and GIAB consulting. The company was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Staffanstorp, Sweden.
